We’re getting ready to bring everyone’s favorite fitness event to sunny San Diego 😎

Fitness for the Caregivers will be in San Diego, CA on Saturday, June 10th at @andazsandiego! 

We start with a guided fitness class (all levels welcome!), followed by a happy hour with your local healthcare community. RSVP today—every attendee gets a goodie bag, 1 free drink, and a plus one. 

Join us at this fun and friendly fitness event sponsored by the amazing @connectrnapp and @thenursingbeat. Reserve your spot at the link in our bio!
